
## 1. Software Requirements

| Component | Purpose | Recommended Version |
|-----------|---------|---------------------|
| **Arduino IDE** | Code writing & uploading to board | **v2.3.2** (latest stable) |
| **Python** | AI chatbot logic / NLP integration | **Python 3.9–3.11** |
| **PySerial** | Python ↔ Arduino serial communication | Latest (`pip install pyserial`) |
| **SpeechRecognition** | Voice input capture | Latest (`pip install SpeechRecognition`) |
| **PyAudio** | Microphone input handling | Compatible with Python version |
| **NLTK / Transformers** | Chatbot AI model | Latest stable release |
| **Arduino Libraries** | Hardware control | Board-specific (Servo, Ultrasonic, etc.) |

---

## 2. Port Number & Communication

- **Default Communication Port (Serial):**
  - **Windows:** Usually `COM3`, `COM4`, `COM5` (Check in *Arduino IDE → Tools → Port*)
  - **Linux/Mac:** `/dev/ttyUSB0` or `/dev/ttyACM0`

- **Baud Rate:**  
  - `9600` (basic projects)  
  - `115200` (high-speed data)

- **Python Side Example:**
```python
import serial
ser = serial.Serial('COM3', 9600)  # Match port & baud rate with Arduino settings
Port Check:

Arduino IDE → Tools → Port → Select Connected Device

3. Version Compatibility
Module/Tool	Compatible With
Arduino Uno	Arduino IDE v1.8.x & v2.x
Arduino Mega	Arduino IDE v1.8.x & v2.x
ESP32/ESP8266	Arduino IDE v2.x + board manager update
Python 3.9+	PySerial, SpeechRecognition, Transformers

4. Extra Software for Chatbot Features
Google Speech API – Voice to text

OpenAI API / Local NLP Model – Text response generation

Optional: Node.js + Socket.io (for web interface)

5. Quick Installation Commands
bash
Always show details

Copy
# Install Python dependencies
pip install pyserial SpeechRecognition pyaudio nltk transformers

# (Optional) For ESP boards in Arduino IDE
# Go to: File → Preferences → Additional Board Manager URLs
# Add: https://dl.espressif.com/dl/package_esp32_index.json
6. Project Notes
Ensure Python version is between 3.9 and 3.11 for compatibility.

Always match the Arduino baud rate with Python code settings.

Keep drivers for your Arduino board installed for smooth serial communication.
